            <title>[LU-9034] Separate the config logs between different MGCs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9034</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When there are more than one MGC, the config log of one MGC should not be used by&lt;br/&gt;
the other MGC, otherwise, the previous MGC won&apos;t be stopped when its using targets&lt;br/&gt;
are down, which cause various problems &lt;/p&gt;</description>
